  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/baab2fff2522f0f69275bf1c25686093.poster.avif?t=1762843963\" width=600 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/baab2fff2522f0f69275bf1c25686093.webm?t=1762843963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/baab2fff2522f0f69275bf1c25686093.mp4?t=1762843963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In PuckOFF you will...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛸️ Put your skates on and play <strong>no rules pond hockey</strong> at local rinks </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚌 Travel around <strong>10 countries </strong>in search for the mysterious Dominator </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏅 Unlock <strong>gear and skills</strong> while trying to figure out how to skate </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏒 Decide <strong>your own playstyle</strong> from classic hockey roles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PuckOFF</strong> immerses players in <strong>street hockey</strong> <i><strong>without rules</strong></i>. The game is designed as a cooperative sports simulator, where you can complete the story campaign alone or with  your friends (up-to 4 in total). Users can partake in a <strong>MASSIVE 32 country-tournament</strong> where only the strongest or the fastest can win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story progresses through levels on a career map, facing opponents of <strong>varying difficulty</strong>. Unlock new equipment and accessories along the way that will rival dominator himself. Players will have to hone their hero's skills along the way, creating builds from <strong>almost 100 different skills</strong> over the course of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/544ae7a989c3afb31e619807d20118e5.poster.avif?t=1762843963\" width=600 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/544ae7a989c3afb31e619807d20118e5.webm?t=1762843963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/544ae7a989c3afb31e619807d20118e5.mp4?t=1762843963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique hockey experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your legacy and rise in the ranks to demolish your opponents while uncovering the story of the ultimate goon. In your travels you will meet new friends and foes, while facing legends that don't play by your rules. Flying sticks, fists, and unfair rules are a sure way to loose the last drops of your sanity.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/1d2a02c47dd2725a5faa54df82109cee.poster.avif?t=1762843963\" width=600 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/1d2a02c47dd2725a5faa54df82109cee.webm?t=1762843963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765990/extras/1d2a02c47dd2725a5faa54df82109cee.mp4?t=1762843963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now <strong>PuckOFF</strong>! (controller is highly recommended) </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Version history</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VERSION 1.0 </strong><i>13.5.2022</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <strong>Campaign</strong> with the first four chapters (+prologue chapter).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> Germany, Switzerland, Slovakia & Czech Republic are first countries to conquer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <strong>Quickplay</strong>  play alone or with your friends using either characters you've created or bosses you've unlocked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> In celebration of hockey world championship games, challenge 40 countries in the new <strong>Tournament-Mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NORDIC VERSION </strong><i>29.5.2022</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added <strong>Sweden</strong> and <strong>Finland</strong> as playable levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added relevant bosses <strong>Captain Crown & Eagle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added relevant levels and story to boot</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOUR DE EAST </strong><i>14.7.2022</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added <strong>China</strong> and <strong>Russia</strong> as playable levels </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added relevant bosses  <strong>Hot Shot</strong> & <strong>Executioner</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added relevant  levels and story to boot</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DOMINATOR UPDATE </strong><i>18.8.2022</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added <strong>North America</strong> as playable levels (Canada & USA) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added relevant bosses <strong>Coyote</strong> & <strong>Hailstorm</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added relevant  levels and story to boot  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Conclusion</strong> for the base storyline   Final matchup</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONTROL SCHEME UPDATE </strong><i>25.10.2024</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Added a 'classic' <strong>NHL-styled controls schema</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Fixed <strong>years</strong> worth of bugs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p>",
